* Determine if any metrics or error logging should be implemented along with your changes.
* Consider tools like New Relic, Sentry, OpenTelemetry, etc.
> If this isn't going to be a large app then it may be best to just use text logs for now. Just make sure there is a limit on how large they are allowed to grow or how long we store old ones.